videos.headline: Ohio's QB Rourke catches a TD pass on trick play
videos.description: Ohio's trick play leads to DL Knock completing a pass to QB Nathan Rourke who dives to make a catch  for a two-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ohio's QB Rourke catches a TD pass on trick play) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: NIU's Childers bolts for 70-yard gain
videos.description: Marcus Childers takes the snap and sprints for a 70-yard gain to put NIU into the red zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (NIU's Childers bolts for 70-yard gain) 2019/10/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ohio OL Pleasants scores a TD
videos.description: Offensive lineman Austen Pleasants catches a pass and runs into the end zone for a two-yard touchdown to give Ohio a 21-10 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ohio OL Pleasants scores a TD) 2019/10/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ohio ties game on Hooks' 47-yard TD
videos.description: Ohio ties the game at 36-36 late in the 4th quarter as Shane Hooks makes a catch and wrestles his way to the end zone for the 47-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ohio ties game on Hooks' 47-yard TD) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: NIU's Richardson makes 37-yard FG to win game
videos.description: NIU's John Richardson nails a 37-yard field goal in the final seconds to seal a 39-36 victory over Ohio.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (NIU's Richardson makes 37-yard FG to win game) 2019/10/12 ESHEET
